Inputs

Performance levels across MPs

These are the necessary columns in the performance data.frame

  • indicator, indicator code
  • year
  • data, computed value
  • iter, iteration number
  • name, indicator name
  • mp, MP name
##        run indicator year      data iter        name  mp
##     1:   1        A1 2034 0.1950018  494    mean(CR) MP1
##     2:   1        A1 2034 0.2198053   75    mean(CR) MP1
##     3:   1        A1 2034 0.1902445  574    mean(CR) MP1
##     4:   1        A1 2034 0.2683732 1420    mean(CR) MP1
##     5:   1        A1 2034 0.2010989  460    mean(CR) MP1
##    ---

Time series of results of MP runs

  • mp, MP name
  • year
  • data, computed value
  • iter, iteration number
  • qname, computed metric, e.g. Catch (C), mean F (F)
